command_info.description: Decide whether you want your XP profile to be public on this server or not.
command_info.name: incognito

incognito.description: Enable or disable incognito on this server.
incognito.name: incognito

disabled.info: From now on you will be listed on the public leaderboard of this server again and the other users can also look at your ranking card.
disabled.title: You have successfully **disabled** the incognito mode!

enabled.info: You will no longer be listed on the public leaderboard of this server and other users will no longer be able to view your ranking card.
enabled.title: You have successfully **enabled** the incognito mode!
